3. Record whether your domain appears as a visible citation
4. Record which competitor domains appear
5. Track changes week-over-week in a simple spreadsheet</p>
<p>This takes 90 minutes per week for 50 keywords. The data is more actionable than any automated tool currently provides.</p>
